Commercial Bank of Kuwait Says Signs Syndicated Loan Agreement

-- B y   F i o n a   M a c D o n a l d
-- 
2011-03-21T10:41:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-21/commercial-bank-of-kuwait-says-signs-syndicated-loan-agreement.html
Commercial Bank of  Kuwait  signed a
syndicated loan with Al-Ghanim International General Trading &
Contracting Co. to finance the second phase of a $1.2 billion
project to expand the country’s Al-Zour South power plant.  The facility was arranged with a group of local and
regional banks, including  Al-Ahli Bank of Kuwait (ABK) ,  Burgan Bank (BURG) 
SAK, Dubai’s  Mashreqbank PSC (MASQ)  and Arab Banking Corp., the Kuwaiti
lender said in an e-mailed statement today. 